# CFOP beginner method

CFOP beginner method consists of 4 steps:

1. **The first cross**
2. **F2L**
3. **2-look OLL**
   1) making the other cross
   2) making the side
4. **2-look PLL**
   1) aligning corners
   2) aligning edges


## **{{accent(text="F2L")}}**

Good video on F2L from **J Perm**: **{{accent(text="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ar_Zit1VLG0",href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ar_Zit1VLG0")}}**


## **{{accent(text="OLL")}}** first step - the cross

| name    | pic        | alg                  |
|---------|:----------:|----------------------|
| **I**   | ![cross i] | **F (R U R' U') F'** |
| **L**   | ![cross l] | **f (R U R' U') f'** |
| **Dot** | ![dot]     | **\[I\] \[L\]**      |


## **{{accent(text="OLL")}}** second step - the side

| name         | pic             | alg                              |
|--------------|:---------------:|----------------------------------|
| **Sune**     | ![oll sune]     | **R U R' U R U2 R'**             |
| **Antisune** | ![oll antisune] | **L' U' L U' L' U2 L**           |
| **H**        | ![oll h]        | **F (R U R' U')3 F'**            |
| **L**        | ![oll l]        | **x (R' U R D') (R' U' R D)**    |
| **T**        | ![oll t]        | **x (L U R' U') (L' U R U')**    |
| **Pi**       | ![oll pi]       | **R U2 (R2 U' R2 U' R2) U2 R**   |
| **U**        | ![oll u]        | **R2 D (R' U2 R) D' (R' U2 R')** |


## **{{accent(text="PLL")}}** first step - align corners

| name                    | pic         | alg                                                |
|-------------------------|:-----------:|----------------------------------------------------|
| **Diagonal**            | ![pll diag] | **(F R U' R' U' R U R' F') (R U R' U' R' F R F')** |
| **Adjacent/Headlights** | ![pll adj]  | **(R U R' U' R' F R2) (U' R' U' R U R' F')**       |


## **{{accent(text="PLL")}}** first step - align edges

| name   | pic       | alg                              |
|--------|:---------:|----------------------------------|
| **Ua** | ![pll ua] | **R U' R U R U R U' R' U' R2**   |
| **Ub** | ![pll ub] | **R2 U R U R' U' R' U' R' U R'** |
| **H**  | ![pll h]  | **M2 U' M2 U2 M2 U' M2**         |
| **Z**  | ![pll z]  | **M' U' M2 U' M2 U' M' U2 M2 U** |
